2013-08-30  John Chapman  <John.Chapman@cern.ch>

	* src/Ibl3DChargeTool.cxx - replaced Hep3Vector with
	CLHEP::Hep3Vector - necessary for CLHEP 2.1.2.3 compatibility.
	* Tagged as PixelDigitization-01-00-02

2013-08-30  Matthew Klein <matthew.henry.klein@cern.ch>

	* Removed dependence on SiDigitization package
	* Combined previous PixelDigitization.* and PixelDigitizationTool.*
	  into PixelDigitizationTool.*. PixelDigitization simply creates
	  and runs the tool.
	* Restructuring of PileUpTools related code to conform to 
	  conventions and simplify the process
	* Removed PixelDigitConfig and the corresponding pointers pixdig
	  in each tool. Each parameter is created and accessed in the 
	  tool or service in which it is used
	* Renamed PixelDistortionsSimpleSurfaceChargesGenerator->
	  SurfaceChargesGenerator.
	* Created a charge generation tool for each technology, which
	  is called by SurfaceChargesTool. 
	* Created CalibSvc and TimeSvc to provide parameters needed
	  by multiple other tools. TimeSvc has the functionality of
	  the old PixelTimeWalkGenerator.
	* Tagged as PixelDigitization-01-00-01

2013-06-24  John Chapman  <John.Chapman@cern.ch>

	* share/PixelDigitization_jobOptions.py - add missing import of
	CfgGetter. 

	* Tagged as PixelDigitization-00-12-05

