	* tagged as PixelDigitization-00-10-01

2010-04-14  John Chapman
	* Add common base class PixelDigitConfig for PixelDigitization and PixelDigitizationTool this deals with all the communication with the other AlgTools in the package and removes the need for two copies of every tool. It also provides a clear list of the 'get' function calls which should be turned into 'set' function calls or DB lookups in the future. Tag this intermediate version before any classes are removed.
	A PixelDigitization/PixelDigitConfig.h
	A src/PixelDigitConfig.cxx
	M PixelDigitization/PixelGangedMerger.h
	M PixelDigitization/SpecialPixelGenerator.h
	M PixelDigitization/PixelDigitizationTool.h
