2009-12-18  Peter Sherwood  <sherwood@pcucl05.cern.ch>

	* Start work on decoupling the various helper classes from
	PixelDigitizationTool. At the same time de-AlgTool where advisable.
	For the moment provide PixelDistortionsSimpleSurfaceChargesGeneratorHelper
	which is to replac PixelDistortionsSimpleSurfaceChargesGeneratorTool

