2009-12-09  Peter Sherwood  <sherwood@pcucl05.cern.ch>

	* Start work on convsersion to Tool based digtization
	Pixel digitization has many helper classes that have references
	to the digitization algorithmm, which makes them unusable in the
	present context. For the moment I make the minimum change: copy the
	code of these classes and change the call back reference to the
	PixelDigitizationTool
	
	A PixelDigitizationTool.h
	A PixelCellDiscriminatorTool.h
	A PixelChargeSmearerTool.h
	A PixelDistortionsSimpleSurfaceChargesGeneratorTool.h
	A PixelNoisyCellGeneratorTool.h
	A PixelDiodeCrossTalkGeneratorTool.h
	A PixelTimeWalkGeneratorTool.h
	A PixelGangedMergerTool.h
	A SpecialPixelGeneratorTool.h

